<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275761>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Photograph of the head and the pronotum of adults of: Protonemura gevi sp. n. (A); P. alcazaba (B); and P. meyeri (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275761/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275762>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Protonemura gevi sp. n. adult. Tip of the male abdomen in ventral view (A); tip of the male abdomen in dorsal view showing the epiproct (B); epiproct in lateral view (C); male paraproct in lateral view (D); tip of the female abdomen in ventral view (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275762/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275763>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Protonemura gevi sp. n. nymph. Head and pronotum in dorsal view (A); gills and first pair of legs in ventral view (B); abdominal tergum (C); female paraproct (D); male paraproct (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275763/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275764>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Diagram of the plan of the cave where Protonemura gevi sp. n. was collected." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

